{"meta":{"title":"TextHexo","subtitle":"","description":"a text hexo project","author":"texter","url":"http://example.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"关于我们","date":"2021-08-24T08:21:47.105Z","updated":"2021-08-24T06:53:21.347Z","comments":true,"path":"about.html","permalink":"http://example.com/about.html","excerpt":"","text":"这是一篇测试博客"},{"title":"categories","date":"2021-08-24T06:47:54.000Z","updated":"2021-08-24T06:48:45.527Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"tags","date":"2021-08-24T06:49:04.000Z","updated":"2021-08-24T06:49:31.196Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"相关链接","date":"2021-08-24T08:22:12.678Z","updated":"2021-08-24T08:19:41.988Z","comments":true,"path":"link.html","permalink":"http://example.com/link.html","excerpt":"","text":"相关链接相关链接"}],"posts":[{"title":"hexo网页显示图片测试文章","slug":"imgtext","date":"2021-08-23T11:55:41.531Z","updated":"2021-08-24T07:47:49.413Z","comments":true,"path":"2021/08/23/imgtext/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2021/08/23/imgtext/","excerpt":"","text":"测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试测试","categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/"},{"name":"buildbolg","slug":"Hexo/buildbolg","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/buildbolg/"}],"tags":[{"name":"texttag1","slug":"texttag1","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag1/"}]},{"title":"hexo发生error：spawn failed错误的解决方法","slug":"spawnfailed","date":"2021-08-22T11:04:07.829Z","updated":"2021-08-24T07:47:59.857Z","comments":true,"path":"2021/08/22/spawnfailed/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2021/08/22/spawnfailed/","excerpt":"","text":"问题描述出现错误error：spawn failed… 问题原因问题大多是因为git进行push或者hexo d的时候改变了一些.deploy_git文件下的内容。 解决方法删除.deploy_git文件夹;在hexo目录于cmd下输入 1git config --global core.autocrlf false 然后，依次执行： 123hexo clean hexo g hexo d","categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/"},{"name":"solveproblem","slug":"Hexo/solveproblem","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/solveproblem/"}],"tags":[{"name":"texttag2","slug":"texttag2","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag2/"}]},{"title":"如何通过修改hosts文件来加速github的访问(Windows)","slug":"girhubhosts","date":"2021-08-22T07:42:38.366Z","updated":"2021-08-24T07:47:53.101Z","comments":true,"path":"2021/08/22/girhubhosts/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2021/08/22/girhubhosts/","excerpt":"","text":"打开DNS查询，切换到DNS选项 查询http://github.com和http://github.global.ssl.fastly.net 选择TTL最小的DNS，复制ip地址，可以多复制几个。找到hosts所在的文件夹Windows 系统位于 C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc\\ 最好把hosts文件备份一下，把hosts文件拷贝一份后改个名即可。 把复制好的IP地址添加到hosts文件中，类似于这个样子 82.113.3 http://github.com 82.113.3 http://github.global.ssl.fastly.net 打开cmd，输入”ipconfig /flushdns”，刷新DNS缓存。","categories":[{"name":"Github","slug":"Github","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Github/"}],"tags":[{"name":"texttag1","slug":"texttag1","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag1/"},{"name":"texttag2","slug":"texttag2","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag2/"}]},{"title":"更换Hexo网页图标","slug":"changeFavicon","date":"2021-08-08T08:02:04.347Z","updated":"2021-08-24T07:39:26.928Z","comments":true,"path":"2021/08/08/changeFavicon/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2021/08/08/changeFavicon/","excerpt":"","text":"说明本文介绍的是主题theme配置文件中的修改方式，也就是说仅适用于被修改的主题。 制作favicon图标1、准备好用作标签页/网页小图标favicon的图片2、搜索favicon 在线，可以看到一些在线图片转favicon的工具3、可以利用这个网站 bitbug 将图片转化为16x16以及32x32的图标 图片位置打开next/source/images，把刚才做好的图标放在这里，命名为favicon16.ico和favicon32.ico 与编辑配置文件打开next主题的_config.yml文件，在favicon:下设置以下内容： favicon:$\\quad$ small: /images/favicon16.ico$\\quad$ medium: /images/favicon32.ico 也就是说当前使用的图标位置路径是主题下的 source/images 。把刚才制作好的图标放到这里。","categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/"},{"name":"solveproblem","slug":"Hexo/solveproblem","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/solveproblem/"}],"tags":[{"name":"texttag1","slug":"texttag1","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag1/"},{"name":"texttag2","slug":"texttag2","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag2/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/"},{"name":"buildbolg","slug":"Hexo/buildbolg","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/buildbolg/"},{"name":"solveproblem","slug":"Hexo/solveproblem","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Hexo/solveproblem/"},{"name":"Github","slug":"Github","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Github/"}],"tags":[{"name":"texttag1","slug":"texttag1","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag1/"},{"name":"texttag2","slug":"texttag2","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/texttag2/"}]}